title: Halloween at the Old Zoo | American Horror Stories - Episode 2: "Rubber (Wo)man - Part Two" (HD)
author: AHS Crave
comment: The Yeah, Yeah, Yeahs backing as a definite enhancement
description:
Ruby (Kaia Gerber) takes Scarlett (Sierra McCormick) to a Halloween party at the abandoned zoo at Griffith Park. Ruby gets possessive of Scarlett after meeting the latter's best friend, Shanti (Belissa Escobedo).
